1. When an instrument is modified in draft mode and not committed, the changes are not visible when the instrument is opened from the record status dashboard.
2. Draft mode	On committing the changes, the changes made in the instruments are reflected when opening the instruments from record status dashboard.
3. On rejecting the changes, the changes made in the instruments are not reflected when opening the instruments from record status dashboard. The changes are still visible when opening the instrument from ‘Designer’.
4. On deleting all the changes, the changes made in the instruments are not reflected when opening the instruments from record status dashboard. The changes are not visible when opening the instrument from ‘Designer’. The changes are deleted permanently